## Example Attribution Formats

### In README.md
```markdown
## Credit

This project is based on [AI Dev Assistant](https://github.com/steeven-louk/ai-dev-assistant) 
by Steeven Loukanou, used under the Attribution License.
```

### In Code Comments
```typescript
/**
 * Based on AI Dev Assistant by Steeven Loukanou
 * https://github.com/steeven-louk/ai-dev-assistant
 * 
 * Modified by: [Your Name]
 * Changes: [What was modified]
 */
```

### In Web Applications
```html
<!-- In footer or about page -->
<p>
  This application is based on 
  <a href="https://github.com/steeven-louk/ai-dev-assistant">
    AI Dev Assistant
  </a> 
  by Steeven Loukanou, used under the Attribution License.
</p>
```

### In GitHub Forks
```markdown
# [Your Project Name]

This project is a fork/derivative of 
[AI Dev Assistant](https://github.com/steeven-louk/ai-dev-assistant) 
by [Steeven Loukanou](https://github.com/steeven-louk)

**Original Project**: Used under the Attribution License
**Changes Made**: [Describe your modifications]
```

