## Attribution Examples for Derivatives

### Example 1: Open Source Fork
```markdown
# MyProject

This is a fork of [AI Dev Assistant](https://github.com/steeven-louk/ai-dev-assistant) 
by Steeven Loukanou.

**Original License**: Attribution License  
**This Project License**: MIT (with original attribution preserved)

## Changes from Original
- [What you changed]
- [What you improved]
- [What you added]

## Acknowledgments
Thanks to Steeven Loukanou for the original AI Dev Assistant project.
```

### Example 2: Commercial Product
```
This product includes software from AI Dev Assistant 
(https://github.com/steeven-louk/ai-dev-assistant) 
© 2026 Steeven Loukanou, used under the Attribution License.

For more information about the original project, visit:
https://github.com/steeven-louk/ai-dev-assistant
```

